<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٥٩ ... سُورَةُ الحَشْرِ ... آياتها ٢٤ ... مدنية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَبَّحَ لِلَّهِ}</span> ... نَزَّهَ اللهَ عَمَّا لَا يَلِيقُ بِهِ جَلَّ جَلَالُهُ وَمَجَّدَهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَهْلِ الْكِتَابِ}</span> ... هُمْ يَهُودُ بَنِي النَّضِيرِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِأَوَّلِ الْحَشْرِ}</span> ... فِي أَوَّلِ إِخْرَاجٍ، وَإِجْلَاءٍ إِلَى الشَّامِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَمْ يَحْتَسِبُوا}</span> ... لَمْ يَخْطُرْ لَهُمْ بِبَالٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَقَذَفَ}</span> ... أَلْقَى.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الرُّعْبَ}</span> ... الخَوْفَ الشَّدِيدَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَا أُولِي الْأَبْصَارِ}</span> ... يَا أَصْحَابَ البَصَائِرِ السَّلِيمَةِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْجَلَاءَ}</span> ... الخُرُوجَ مِنْ دِيَارِهِمْ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{شَاقُّوا}</span> ... خَالَفُوا أَشَدَّ المُخَالَفَةِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِّينَةٍ}</span> ... نَخْلَةٍ، أَوْ نَوْعٍ مِنَ النَّخْلِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أُصُولِهَا}</span> ... سَاقِهَا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَلِيُخْزِيَ}</span> ... لِيُذِلَّ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمَا أَفَاء اللَّهُ}</span> ... وَمَا رَدَّهُ اللهُ مِنْ أَمْوَالِ بَنِي النَّضِيرِ،<span class="c5"> وَالفَيْءُ:</span> مَا أُخِذَ مِنْ أَمْوَالِ الكُفَّارِ بِحَقٍّ، مِنْ غَيْرِ قِتَالٍ،<span class="c5"> وَالغَنِيْمَةُ:</span> مَا أُخِذَ بِقِتَالٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَمَا أَوْجَفْتُمْ}</span> ... فَلَمْ تَرْكَبُوا لِتَحْصِيلِهِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رِكَابٍ}</span> ... مَا يُرْكَبُ مِنَ الإِبِلِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>